    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "John Moneymaker stopped at Kerr Hollow gate where I was on duty October 15, 1950,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "3:20 P.M. He and I observed what appeared to be a skywriter in the air. He was one-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "quarter of the way through a letter \"O\". The object appeared to be 12,000 to 15,000",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "feet high and east by north of the gate, approximately one mile distance from the gate.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "At this time, the size appeared to be about the size of a four or five passenger plane.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "The object had a smoke trail the same crosssectional size of its body and about one-",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "quarter of a mile long. The smoke was grayish in color. The color of the body of the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "object was silver metallic. The object gave off no reflection. It was dull in appear-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "ance. When first observed, it was describing an arc toward the ground. When the",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "object failed to complete the outside loop, I went into the gate house to report its",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "appearance. Up till this time I thought it to be a plane doing some skywriting. While",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "I was making the phone call, [REDACTED] watched the object continue downward to",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "1,500 feet. At that altitude, a second object was noticed alongside the smoke trail.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "The second object was the same size and shape and was about 50 feet behind the first",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "object. The second object appeared to be attached to the first object's smoke trail",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "with about an 80 degree forward thrust, yet the second object was moving in the same",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "direction of the first object and not drawing away from the smoke trail of the first",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "object the way it should have been doing according to its angle and direction. At",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "this altitude, both objects changed from a bullet shape to a bladder shape. Also, at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "1500 feet both objects began pulling out of the vertical dive. During the entire",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "descent, both objects diminished in size. From 1,500 feet, the angle of descent was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "about 45 degrees. At about 500 feet, the second or trailing object disappeared. The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "object continued downward to a point north of the perimeter fence over the roadway",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "about 60 yards from the gatehouse toward Solway bridge. This was where the object was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "when I came out of the gatehouse. At this time, the object had diminished to about 2x5",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "inches.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
